These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, traveling, collecting, hiking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, horror, martial-arts, epic
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, rowing, soccer, cricket
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, snowmobile, van, helicopter
 1. the person who's sport is rowing is not to the right of the person who's sport is sailing##8
 2. the person driving the quad-bike is not to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##8
 3. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##8
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is not to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##8
 6. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is reading##5
 8. the person watching epic movies is between the person driving the snowmobile and the person who's sport is rowing##2
 9. the person driving the helicopter is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
10. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
11. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
12. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##5
13. the person watching martial-arts movies is not to the left of the person driving the helicopter##8
14. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person driving the van##1
15. the person who's hobby is traveling is not the person who's sport is rowing##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | reading     | traveling   | hiking | collecting |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | epic   | musical   | martial-arts  |
| Sport         | rowing  | soccer  | cricket  | sailing |
| Transport     | quad-bike    | van | snowmobile     | helicopter    |

