.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk, tea, almond-milk
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, lettuce, cauliflower, pear
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, dubstep, ambient, country
4 different pets are kept: turtle, hamster, fish, ferret
 1. the fan of ambient is between the owner of the turtle and the fan of dubstep##2
 2. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the right of the owner of the hamster##8
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person eating watermelon##3
 4. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
 5. the owner of the turtle is not to the left of the fan of dubstep##8
 6. the person eating pear is not to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##8
 7. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the ferret##5
 8. the owner of the fish is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of techno is the owner of the hamster##1
10. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
11. the owner of the turtle is not to the left of the fan of ambient##8
12. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
13. the fan of country is somewhere to the right of the person eating lettuce##5
14. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the fan of ambient##3
15. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
17. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the fan of dubstep##8
18. the person eating lettuce is not to the right of the owner of the hamster##8
19. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | tea | almond-milk  | soy-milk  |
| Food          | pear     | lettuce | watermelon | cauliflower  |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep    | ambient  | country | techno |
| Pet           | fish | ferret | turtle    | hamster  |

