 3. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the left of the person watching sports movies##5
 4. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the right of the fan of ambient##5
 5. the person who's sport is rowing is not to the right of the person watching family movies##8
 6. the person who's hobby is drawing is not to the left of the person watching crime movies##8
 7. the fan of reggae is in an odd position##4
 8. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
 9. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
10. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far right##1
11. the person watching family movies is not to the left of the fan of classical##8
12. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3

