 9. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the social-worker##1
10. the designer is the person who's sport is handball##1
11. the person who's sport is badminton is not to the right of the person eating peach##8
12. the lawyer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
13. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
14. the designer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
