 4. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5
 5. the person driving the car is the turkish##1
 6. the person drinking juice is not to the right of the indian##8
 7. the person drinking lemonade is not the polish##6
 8. the bartender is somewhere between the person driving the car and the person drinking lemonade##7
 9. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the bartender##5
10. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the bartender##3
11. the librarian is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
12. the bartender is not the australian##6
13. the indian is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
14. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
15. the person driving the helicopter is not to the right of the bartender##8

.:: Answer ::.
