.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, sprite, cola, 7up
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, funk, metal, classical
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, handball, badminton, sailing
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, trike, ship, helicopter
 1. the person drinking cola is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 3. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person driving the helicopter##5
 4. the person drinking fanta is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
 6. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
 7. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
 8. the person driving the trike is not to the right of the person who's sport is handball##8
 9. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
10. the person drinking sprite is not to the right of the fan of funk##8
11. the fan of metal is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
12. the person driving the helicopter is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of metal is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | fanta   | 7up     | cola    | sprite |
| Music-Genre   | salsa  | classical      | metal     | funk     |
| Sport         | biathlon | badminton  | sailing     | handball  |
| Transport     | skateboard     | ship | helicopter | trike     |

