The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, blues, ambient, house
 1. the person who's hobby is fishing is not to the left of the mechanic##8
 2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 3. the fan of house is somewhere to the right of the fan of ambient##5
 4. the librarian is the person watching crime movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not the paramedic##6
 6. the person watching superhero movies is not to the right of the fan of blues##8
 7. the person watching fantasy movies is not to the left of the paramedic##8
 8. the paramedic is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
 9. the fan of ambient is in an even position##4
10. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
11. the person watching superhero movies is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the paramedic and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
13. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left or far right##3

